author: bayard
msg: Applying third patch from LANG-381. Fixes the minimum(float[]) type methods to correctly return NaN when it is in the array, and adds an IEEE754rUtils class that obeys the IEEE 754r update in which NaN in min/max methods should be ignored unless all values are NaN.
